title: lar:///ha.ka.ba/@lararium/tw5/tiddlers/sigil-widget
tags: $:/tags/Global lar:///ha.ka.ba/tags/SharktoothSigil
lar-kind: pragma-alias
lar-pono-uri: lar:///ha.ka.ba/@lares/api/v0.1/pono/widget
lar-alias-for: \widget
lar-open-pattern: <<~\s*\\widget\s+([\w~-]+)(?:\s+([^>]*?))?\s*>>
lar-close-pattern: <<~\/\\widget\s*>>
type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki

<!-- \widget — English alias for the TW5 \widget pragma.
     No direct Hawaiian equivalent; the ~ prefix is the Lares convention.

     <<~ \widget ~name(params) >>body<<~/ \widget >> declares a named widget
     callable as <<~name ...>> via the ~ dispatcher.
     lar-kind: pragma-alias — produces no render output; the sigil serves as the declaration.

     The ~ prefix convention: <<~ \widget ~mana(uri:"") >>...<<~/ \widget >>
     registers a new mana sigil callable as <<~ mana lar:///uri >>. -->
